welcome_message_body: Welcome to Highland City, where the mountains meet the sea! Immerse yourself in our charming city known for its stunning natural beauty and vibrant culture. We invite you to explore and enjoy all that Highland City has to offer.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Bartow Airport houses all check-in counters, baggage claim, and security checkpoints.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Bartow Airport serves private and charter flights, with amenities such as lounges and private hangars.

wifi.note: WiFi is available throughout the airport terminal and general aviation areas.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Municipal Airport handles all commercial flights and is equipped with modern amenities for passenger convenience.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Municipal Airport caters to private and charter flights, providing a comfortable and efficient experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free WiFi throughout the airport terminal.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Gilbert Field Airport serves all domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Gilbert Field Airport handles all freight and cargo operations.

wifi.note: Passengers can access free WiFi throughout the airport terminal.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Zephyrhills Airport serves domestic flights and offers a variety of amenities for travelers.

terminals.name: General Aviation Terminal
terminals.description: The general aviation terminal at Zephyrhills Airport caters to private and corporate flights, providing a comfortable and convenient experience for passengers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport for all passengers.
